Show HN: ChatGPT – Lets talk – Chrome extension thats adds voice to ChatGPT
text:
Now updated with the ability to change the voice of the AI. Select from 100+ different voices. Additionally, you can even change the pitch and the rate of the words spoken. All done using native Javascript and features available in Chrome locally.

- Features:

* Minimalist UI (almost none) and small size just 18.13KiB.

* Works with only keyboard shortcuts. Talk to and hear from ChatGPT.

* Created with native JavaScript with features available in the browser, no external libraries or API/network calls.
